This is because id is "common initialism" as it's called in golint's [source code](https://github.com/golang/lint/blob/9bad2ac064ef73cba57dec90e67d45fec2ab67bc/lint.go#L716). Maybe go swagger can copy the code as lintName is not exported. Or even better if golint's lintName gets exported and then is used by go swagger.
